        "onboarding_pflanzen_blase": ["de": "Such dir zwei Pflanzen aus, die du heute pflanzen möchtest.", "en": "Pick two plants you'd like to plant today.", "es": "Elige dos plantas que te gustaría plantar hoy.", "fr": "Choisis deux plantes que tu aimerais planter aujourd'hui.", "it": "Pick two plants you'd like to plant today.", "pt": "Escolhe duas plantas que gostarias de plantar hoje."],
